We recommended the following:

a. Create an inspection and appraisal team to conduct a complete physical inventory of all assets owned by the Municipality;
b. Maintain and update property tags and stock/property cards by the Property Custodian;
c. Exert more efforts to secure the documents of properties not provided with depreciation;
d. Identify unserviceable properties and record the same in the Inventory and Inspection Report of Unserviceable Property to facilitate the disposal and eventual dropping from the books; and
e. Transfer all completed projects to General Fund and subject the same to depreciation.
